        <item>
            <title>一條蛇令日本新幹線列車停駛，蛇纏繞高壓電線引致停電</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/30/hebi-shinkansen/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hebi-shinkansen</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/30/hebi-shinkansen/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 30 Apr 2025 15:49:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305551</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本東海道新幹線在 4 月 30 日傍晚突然出現供電異常，影響「新大阪－名古屋」及「新大阪－東京」兩段列車運行，所幸在電力恢復及安全確認後約一小時內逐步回復正常。調查顯示，事故源頭竟是一條蛇爬上高壓電線，導致短路，引發整段列車系統癱瘓。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430354screensh.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305554" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430354screensh-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430354screensh-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430354screensh.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430214screensh.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305555" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430214screensh-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430214screensh-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430214screensh.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>事故發生於當地時間下午 5 時 25 分左右，位於岐阜縣內岐阜羽島與米原站之間區間出現停電，直接令新幹線主要路線運作受阻。根據 JR 東海透露，當時在大垣市靜裏町有蛇接觸架空電纜，引發短路。由於事發地點是列車密集行駛路段，電力異常迫使多班列車緊急停駛。</p><p>在 JR 名古屋站，旅客面對突如其來的中斷，紛紛湧向職員查詢情況，不少乘客受困月台。雖然晚間 7 時已陸續恢復通車，但班次調動持續受影響，整體列車運作一度陷入混亂。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430454screensh.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305556" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430454screensh-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430454screensh-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/gw2025430454screensh.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>日本電視台報道指出，這次事故讓人聯想到新幹線電力系統對外來生物幹擾的脆弱性。儘管 JR 東海快速查明原因並迅速回復供電，但事件仍突顯新幹線網絡在極端與偶發因素下的潛在風險。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_64731"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OchdVUDSalQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/30/hebi-shinkansen/fun-tech/">一條蛇令日本新幹線列車停駛，蛇纏繞高壓電線引致停電</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
