        <item>
            <title>打麻雀機械人登場，機械臂打牌 + 能自主研判牌局</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/30/majongrobot/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=majongrobot</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/30/majongrobot/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 30 Apr 2025 12:35:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305535</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>平時放假最慘是三缺一無腳一齊打牌。現在中國人工智能公司靈初智能科技公司 PsiBot 展示了一個具備高階推理、長程操作能力的機械人 Psi-R1。機械人能在變化快速、環境開放的現實場景中打麻雀，並展現靈活操作和自主決策能力。PsiBot 利用自主研發的分層端到端模型 Psi-R1，結合類人推理方式與強化學習框架，成功實現 CoAT（Chain of Action Thought）思維系統，並在麻雀桌上執行出牌、碰牌與胡牌等策略性決策。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir108screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir108screenshot-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir108screenshot-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir108screenshot.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Psi-R1 在最新展示中透過感應器進行精細操作，準確抓取和翻動麻雀牌，其動作節奏雖慢，但整體過程與人類玩家極為相似。機械人不單只執行物理動作，更可進行連貫的邏輯推理。每次出牌前，Psi-R1 都會經歷完整思考流程，包括判斷手中牌面組合、計算風險與收益、預測對手出牌，再決定是否執行碰牌、槓牌或胡牌操作。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1028screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305538" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1028screensho-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1028screensho-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1028screensho.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1048screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1048screensho-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1048screensho-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1048screensho.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在 PsiBot 的影片中，Psi-R1 能根據對手出的一筒判斷自己擁有兩張一筒，具備碰牌資格，因此執行碰牌行動，目標是加快聽牌進程。其判斷邏輯包括：「從我手牌來看，不應該爭取清一色，碰是目前為胡牌作最好準備。」這一思考程序讓機械人能如人類般審視局勢，自主調整戰術。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1057screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305536" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1057screensho-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1057screensho-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1057screensho.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>更特別的是，Psi-R1 能在遊戲進行中變更策略。例如原定打出六筒，但抽到七筒後，計算條牌牌型已成順子，自行改變計劃並宣佈自摸胡牌。這樣的決策過程説明機械人不僅擁有記憶和模擬人腦思維能力，更能在實時互動中適應變化，作出合適行動。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1120screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305537" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1120screensho-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1120screensho-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1120screensho.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>PsiBot 表示，這項技術展示機械人已達到 L3 等級的智慧行動能力，可支援複雜多變的場景操作。麻將只是其應用案例之一，未來目標是將該系統應用至工業生產、零售服務、物流配送和家居環境等領域，發揮長時間穩定執行的潛力。</p><p>除了單機能力外，Psi-R1 亦展現人-機、機-機與機-環境三重交互協作的功能。影片中，兩部 PsiBot 機械人能彼此溝通、交換資訊並協作完成打牌任務，提升整體策略智慧。當中機械人甚至能模擬情緒表情，增加牌桌互動性。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir119screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305542" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir119screenshot-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir119screenshot-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir119screenshot.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1128screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1128screensho-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1128screensho-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1128screensho.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>PsiBot 期望透過麻將這項複雜遊戲，向大眾呈現其機械人在自主學習、長時推理及人類級操作能力上的進展。這一突破令「三缺一」的情況或許再不是問題，未來打麻雀可能有機械人自動上桌應戰。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_21222"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OfwtXkvRuEQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：YouTube</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/30/majongrobot/fun-tech/">打麻雀機械人登場，機械臂打牌 + 能自主研判牌局</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
